ComicInfo.Summary: By Steven "Noppie" Knopenberger; from the creator of Crystal Balls comes this luscious tale of big-breasted bi-chicks in outer space, staging hot, sweaty orgies against a starry backdrop -- all drawn with Noppie's lush art style, meticulous attention to detail and moment-by-moment storytelling techniques!
